Package: RHive
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2017-11-16
Title: Run R Code Through Apache Hive
Authors@R: person("Clark", "Fitzgerald", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "clarkfitzg@gmail.com")
Author: Clark Fitzgerald [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Clark Fitzgerald <clarkfitzg@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0), whisker
Suggests: roxygen2,
    testthat
Description: RHive facilitates writing R code to run on data stored
    in Apache Hive.
It requires a working Hive cluster with R installed
    on each node.
